OL,3,CFather of man killed in atrocity speak
OL,4,Cof toll of Omagh bomb
OL,6,FThe inquiry heard that Aiden shared
OL,7,Fhis birthday with his grandfather,
OL,8,FJohn O'Connor, and that there was
OL,9,Fexactly 60 years between them.
OL,11,FThe pair had developed a "special
OL,12,Fbond" and always celebrated their
OL,13,Fbirthdays together.
OL,15,F"It was something that was very
OL,16,Fspecial for both of them," Mr
OL,17,FGallagher said.
OL,19,F"It was something that we always
OL,20,Fvalued and we know his granddad valued
OL,21,Fit."
OL,26,@sD@ZOUtD@EO]wD@AOUxD@ZO]{D@AOU}D@DO]
