OL,3,CFather of man killed in atrocity speak
OL,4,Cof toll of Omagh bomb
OL,6,FMr Gallagher said that John was a
OL,7,Fdifferent person after the bomb and
OL,8,Fthat he died 11 days after Aiden's
OL,9,Fdeath. The family believe his death is
OL,10,Fdirectly linked to Aiden's killing.
OL,12,FMr Gallagher said the family were a
OL,13,Fclose unit as they spent so much time
OL,14,Ftogether through the family business
OL,15,Fincluding running a cafe and limousine
OL,16,Fand taxi business.
OL,18,FHe said that Aiden had a strong work
OL,19,Fethic.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
