OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F441A1738689662
OL,3,CFather of man killed in atrocity speak
OL,4,Cof toll of Omagh bomb
OL,6,F"He was always somebody that knew the
OL,7,Fimportance of doing things and doing
OL,8,Fthem right and as he got older, he
OL,9,Fenjoyed doing what he'd done, but he
OL,10,Falso felt that it had to be done
OL,11,Fright," he added.
OL,13,FHe said that Aiden developed a love
OL,14,Ffor vehicles and engines from an early
OL,15,Fage.
OL,17,F"He was a normal young person. He
OL,18,Fwould have went out at the weekend
OL,19,Fwith his friends. They enjoyed having
OL,20,Fa beer and having fun," he added.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@GO]yD@AOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/17
