OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F441A1738689662
OL,3,CFather of man killed in atrocity speak
OL,4,Cof toll of Omagh bomb
OL,6,F"Cars were absolutely the main
OL,7,Finterest in his life but it wasn't the
OL,8,Fonly interest.
OL,10,FAiden had a wide group of friends who
OL,11,Fcame from different backgrounds, which
OL,12,Fwas particularly evident during his
OL,13,Fwake and funeral.
OL,15,F"We live in a country that there's a
OL,16,Flot of division, bigotry on both
OL,17,Fsides, but we never allowed that to
OL,18,Fpenetrate our family," he added.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/17
