OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F441A1738689662
OL,3,CFather of man killed in atrocity speak
OL,4,Cof toll of Omagh bomb
OL,6,F"We chose our friends because of the
OL,7,Fcontent of their heart, not because of
OL,8,Ftheir religion or their politics, and
OL,9,Fthat was an example that we gave to
OL,10,Four children."
OL,12,FHe said that Aiden was the joker of
OL,13,Fhis friendship group.
OL,15,F"There's no question about it. He
OL,16,Fenjoyed fun. He enjoyed company,
OL,17,Fenjoyed being with people.
OL,19,F"He was fun to be with. He was
OL,20,Fsensitive to others."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@NO]wD@AOU{D@AOU|D@UO]
