OL,4,Cof toll of Omagh bomb
OL,6,FAiden also shared a special bond with
OL,7,Fhis mother, Patsy.
OL,9,FThe inquiry was told that she dealt
OL,10,Fwith Aiden's killing "inwardly".
OL,12,F"I don't know where she got the
OL,13,Fenergy. Given that her father died 11
OL,14,Fdays after that, I think it shows the
OL,15,Fstrong character that she is, that she
OL,16,Fcould manage that. I personally found
OL,17,Fit very difficult to deal with but she
OL,18,Fseemed to cope," Mr Gallagher added.
OL,26,@rD@VOUrD@_O]tD@AOUzD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/17
