PN,44116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F441A1738689662
OL,3,CFather of man killed in atrocity speak
OL,4,Cof toll of Omagh bomb
OL,6,F"I could not allow myself to believe
OL,7,Fhe was dead. I even convinced myself
OL,8,Fthat he never existed, and at times I
OL,9,Fcouldn't even remember what he looked
OL,10,Flike, as though I was watching a movie.
OL,12,F"I was disconnected to what was
OL,13,Fhappening around me, I felt like this
OL,14,Ffor a very long time.
OL,16,F"I have often asked if it's better to
OL,17,Fbe the victim or the survivor,
OL,18,Fsomething that can never be fully
OL,19,Fanswered and changes depending on
OL,20,Fmood."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU|D@FO]
